{"tid":1640102,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你班人唔係好醒既咩？點解仲討論個的士狗？","createTime":"2019-10-09T00:16:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T03:10:09.000Z","uid":99805,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fe8ca7d63be303cf12f3932fdc9c67aecccf3264","tid":1640102,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:16:50.000Z","msg":"今朝訓醒仲見到有熱門post講的士狗<br />\n你地唔係好鍾意屌人帶風向既咩？<br />\n點解比人牽住個鼻咁多日都唔屌？<br />\n<br />\n咩人最想你地張個焦點放係對警察有利既事上面不停討論？我地無晒文宣？無晒其他焦點？<br />\n<br />\n一家三口被指非法集結<br />\n拘捕父母遺下幾歲細路<br />\n公屋無地位<br />\n廢鐵荔枝角炒車<br />\n<br />\n琴晚單蒙面黑警上水站嫁禍有排玩啦<br />\n仲有浮屍，831，721呢？<br />\n由其831，721，大家都只係講個數字<br />\n我地應該日日都深入探討<br />\n<br />\n班狗越唔想提唔想講我地更加要講<br />\n佢地提既，我地少少都唔好再應<br />\n<br />\n我預左有人屌我分化，帶風向<br />\n不過如果你唔係鬼，係真正既巴打<br />\n諗一諗我有無講錯"},{"pid":"aef4141e2954e26042546d1bd6a69fdec2b9209d","tid":1640102,"uid":99805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:18:36.000Z","msg":"補充<br />\n<br />\n我地根本唔需要樣樣都回應到咁清晰<br />\n係呢方面我地應該學下班狗<br />\n扮傻扮睇唔到<br />\n由鳩得佢地自己講<br />\n<br />\n我地就日日將佢地難辭其咎既事放大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a279227bb3012a7179bb8fd812229dc8dfeb4daf","tid":1640102,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e087dec1c440a4545753474a4ef2f9c8a9c19d08","tid":1640102,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:19:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcf2e56c3948309d2c71cbb82b04d2f5831c2f11","tid":1640102,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:20:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f523a3cf44f8dba7c3ee144301db95524f0aca","tid":1640102,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:20:49.000Z","msg":"<img